\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 rder of Oddfellows. There's other Oddfellows beside this but this is a Manchester Unity Order of Oddfellows. And it was the Rising Sun Lodge, East - in the Eastwood area}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid729553\charrsid15805719 , you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719  see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7670325 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 And he was quite an active member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13597539 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7670325 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 Was he a member of any other kind of savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13597539 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7670325 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 A funeral club or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13597539 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7670325 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10891958\charrsid15805719 Boot club?
